            ; the prisoner was in our service on the 9th of August, and on the 10th I gave her in charge; she said nothing to me - she said she had lent the articles to her brother, to keep him dry, as it rained hard, but that was not stated to me - she was a year and eight months with us.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-126-person1311">
                  WALTER 
                  LEY
