                     <interp inst="t18270913-126-person1311" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I produce a cloak and shawl, which I got from the prisoner's brother - I found the prisoner in the watch-house; she said she lent the cloak and shawl to her brother, and he had pawned the other articles, which she had given him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270913-126-person1312">
                  JOHN 
                  BRANSOM
