                     <interp inst="t18270913-126-person1312" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the prisoner's brother; she gave me the shawl and cloak - I had been out of work, and asked her for 4s. - she said she had no money, but would give me a cloak and whittle of her own, which I pawned for 4s.</p>
